Feature: Restaurants
  In order decide where to get some food
  As a user
  I want to see restaurant reviews

  Scenario: View critic reviews
    Given I go to "/restaurant/test-restaurant/"
    I should see critic reviews

  Scenario: View user reviews
    Given I go to "/restaurant/test-restaurant/review/savants/"
    I should see user reviews

  Scenario: View friend reviews
    Given I am logged in
    And I go to "/restaurant/test-restaurant/review/friends/"
    I should see friend reviews
